title: #92Noon Radio Row Day 2!: Wobby/Florio/Leber/Pace/Finley/Bruno
description: PA, Nordo, and Wobby are back on Super Bowl 52's Radio Row! Mike Florio starts out the show, Ben Leber returns, Orlando Pace adds HOF cred to the program, Jermichael Finley talks about his tweets and other things, and Tony Bruno tries to defend Eagles fans.
